FBIS4-52435 "dreas090_c_94032" FBIS-EAS-94-090 Daily Report 10 May 1994 North Korea Kim Il-song Sends Wreath Upon Death of Deputy Kim Il-song Sends Wreath Upon Death of Deputy SK1005051994 Pyongyang KCNA in English 0419 GMT 10 May 94 SK1005051994 Pyongyang KCNA English BFN [Text] Pyongyang, May 10 (KCNA) -- The great leader President Kim Il-song Monday sent a wreath to the bier of Yi Tong-chun, member of the Central Committee of the Workers' Party of Korea and deputy to the Supreme People's Assembly of the Democratic People's Republic of Korea, expressing deep condolences over his death. Yi Tong-chun died on May 8 at the age of 61. He devotedly worked at responsible posts of central and local party organizations and party organizations of the army to defend the party and the leader and firmly build up the party ranks.
